description:
Are you engaged in a fulfilling life, moving toward a compelling goal?

Some people have a natural ability to know what they want, and pursue it with drive and conviction. Taking one bold step after another, they don’t seem to hesitate or second-guess themselves, have no lack of self-confidence, and gain satisfaction and positive growth wherever they apply themselves.

Others find themselves mired in a holding pattern of self-doubt, confusion, and lack of self-confidence. Never getting what they want, or even knowing what that might be, they feel stuck, frustrated, and unfulfilled.

This three week course provides the focus, training, and support you need to define your direction, overcome self-doubt and lack of self-confidence, and map your steps forward in life. If you’ve been feeling stuck, and ready for a change, use this course to gain clarity, get traction, and clear your path ahead.
title: Transform Self Doubt into Confidence
